with (at least) the following in the commit message:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This closes #4924&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;commit 97620649ddfcf8f0320b20bdfdb69d9b44dd8f0c&lt;br/&gt;
Author: Bart&#322;omiej Tartanus &amp;lt;bartektartanus@gmail.com&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
